OL,3,CInvestigations launched in crackdown
OL,4,Con unlicensed Botox products
OL,6,FCriminal investigations have been
OL,7,Flaunched as part of a crackdown on
OL,8,Funlicensed Botox products, the
OL,9,Fmedicines regulator said after it
OL,10,Ffound untrained sellers offering
OL,11,Ftreatments in bedrooms and kitchens.
OL,13,FThe Medicine and Healthcare Products
OL,14,FRegulator Agency (MHRA) said it
OL,15,Flaunched several investigations
OL,16,Ffollowing a spike in hospital
OL,17,Fadmissions believed to be linked to
OL,18,Fthe use of unlicensed botulinum toxin
OL,19,Fproducts, often referred to as Botox.
