OL,3,CInvestigations launched in crackdown
OL,4,Con unlicensed Botox products
OL,6,FThe regulator warned that anyone
OL,7,Fcaught selling or supplying unlicensed
OL,8,Fbotulinum toxin faces up to two years
OL,9,Fin prison and unlimited fines.
OL,11,FAndy Morling, head of the MHRA's
OL,12,FCriminal Enforcement Unit, said:
OL,13,F"Criminals are exploiting the
OL,14,Fpopularity of cosmetic treatments by
OL,15,Fpeddling dangerous, unlicensed
OL,16,Fproducts, putting profit before safety.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
