OL,3,CInvestigations launched in crackdown
OL,4,Con unlicensed Botox products
OL,6,F"Anyone involved in the supply of
OL,7,Funlicensed botulinum toxin ` whether
OL,8,Fthrough organised networks or informal
OL,9,Fsales from kitchen tables, hair
OL,10,Fsalons, or via social media ` is
OL,11,Fbreaking the law and endangering lives.
OL,13,F"The 41 individuals we've seen between
OL,14,FJune and August left seriously ill,
OL,15,Frepresent the devastating human cost
OL,16,Fof this trade.
OL,18,F"We are working across the country to
OL,19,Fidentify those responsible, seize
OL,20,Fillegal products, and bring cases to
OL,21,Fcourt.
